- "Elixirs are still blooming" refers to beverages that are marked as 'Active';
- "Sections" refers to the categories of beverages;
- "Reimagined" refers to the number of versions each beverage has.

- 'view' refers to the action of accessing a beverage's information;
- 'version_number > 1' indicates that the version is not the initial version;
- 'version_date' is the date when a specific version of a beverage's information was created.

